  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Chevy GMC Silverado, Sierra, Tahoe, Yukon 4.8L, 5.3L, 6.0L, 6.2L</li>\n  <li>Chevy GMC 2002-2013 Tahoe, Yukon, Suburban, Escalade 4.8L, 5.3L V8</li>\n  <li>Chevy GMC 2007-2013 Tahoe, Yukon, Suburban, Escalade SUV 6.0L, 6.2L</li>\n  <li>Chevy GMC 2007-2013 Silverado, Sierra 1500/2500 Truck 6.0L, 6.2L</li>\n  <li>Chevy GMC 2002-2013 Silverado, Sierra Pickup Truck 4.8L, 5.3L V8</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance</li>\n  <li>Shorty design for power gain from idle to mid-range RPM</li>\n  <li>Fully mandrel bent tubes made of high quality 16-gauge Mild Steel</li>\n  <li>Head flanges laser-cut from high quality 3/8-inch thick steel plates</li>\n  <li>The flange is flattened by a hydraulic press for precise and leak free sealing</li>\n  <li>All joints are golden color TIG brass style welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n  <li>Flanges chrome plated for corrosion resistance</li>\n  <li>Black paint coating, can withstand up to 500°F</li>\n  <li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n  <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Header Type:</strong> Shorty / Short Tube</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Primary Diameter:</strong> 1-7/8 in.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Collector Diameter:</strong> 2-1/2 in.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Head Flange Thickness:</strong> 3/8 in. (9.5mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Pipe Thickness:</strong> 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> Mild Steel</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Finish:</strong> Black Paint</li>\n</ul>\n",
